						<p class="text-sm mt-1">Developed expertise in algorithm design and analysis, including complexity evaluation, optimization techniques, and rigorous assessment of algorithmic efficiency across diverse computational problems.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-4">
